GET THE LOOK:
1. Gather hair half up using @tresemme micro mist hairspray in extend and a smoothing brush
2. Use @bumbleandbumble sumo wax and a toothbrush to brush hairline 
3. Repeat in bottom section of hair, spraying more hairspray at roots then brushing upwards
4. Attach braiding hair to a string then tie to the base of the pony
5. Tie the hair around the base to conceal the elastic, then French braid the first 3 rotations of hair with natural hair
6. Feed in more hair as you continue the braid
7. Secure ends with an elastic to finish
